<p>My first really long-ish tale, for DrChandra's Dread &amp; Circuses canon! This piece is meant to answer a question I had while reading over some of it. If the circus performs for people of all different worlds and planes, how do they retain their 'disquieting' aspect when what they're doing in another realm might come off as&#8230; normal?<br />
